      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This exceptional unit offers a refined driving experience, featuring a preserved interior and a robust powertrain that ensures long-term reliability. A premier choice for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of sophisticated performance and proven value in a pre-owned executive vehicle.",
