    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is in really solid shape, just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. It drives like a dream and has been well-loved. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with documented subframe reinforcement plates, and the Vanos unit has been overhauled to ensure precise variable valve timing. Riding on staggered Style 67 wheels, the suspension geometry remains true with crisp turn-in and minimal bushing deflection. A mechanically robust specimen that balances raw, naturally aspirated performance with iconic M-division engineering.",
      "price": 32800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs smoothly.",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
