    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example that balances performance with daily utility. The exterior finish maintains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical for a car of this age. The interior is exceptionally clean, featuring premium upholstery that shows only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat. All cabin electronics, from the infotainment system to the heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, with a comprehensive service log showing regular interval maintenance. Recent work includes a fresh set of tires and a coolant flush. It drives straight, brakes firmly without pulsation, and offers a comfortable, rattle-free ride. This is a solid, reliable car that has been treated with respect by its previous owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
