      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it's looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip! It\u2019s in solid shape and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so you can drive away with a smile! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why I've loved owning this car!",
      "price": 32500.0,
